  </sponsors>
  <source>Novartis</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will assess the safety and efficacy of ACZ885 on stimulated C-peptide during a
      mixed meal test in patients with newly-diagnosed type 1 diabetes mellitus.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
